# Kotlin
.kotlin/

# Verify-lane binary evidence (screenshots, reports, page sources). The RECEIPT
# (qa/evidence/latest.json) IS committed — these artifacts are hashed into it instead.
qa-artifacts/

# Verify-lane receipt history — a LOCAL rolling window (last 30 runs) the studio
# console's Evidence timeline reads. latest.json remains the committed
# receipt-of-record; this local log is not committed (and is excluded from the
# inputs hash like the rest of qa/evidence).
qa/evidence/history/

